Title: Hard Counter
Description:
We've managed to get some Demolishers on the beach, but the stupid dwarves are also out there with their stupid mortar tubes, preventing the Demolishers from pushing forward and assaulting the keep itself!

Get out there, kill some dwarves, and blow up some mortar tubes.
ObjectivesText: Kill 8 Lion's Landing Mortar Team Engineers and destroy 2 Lion's Landing Mortar Tubes.
